"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Panel A) The normal nailfold capillaroscopic pattern, showing regular disposition of the capillary loops along the nail bed (original magnification 200x, M. Cutolo). Panel B) A decreased number of loops should be considered highly specific for secondary Raynaud's phenomenon and induce 'desertification' of the nail bed (original magnification 200x, M. Cutolo).",
