"     Gelcap, oral: 500 mg",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Mapap&reg;: 500 mg",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Gelcap, rapid release, oral: 500 mg",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Tylenol&reg; Extra Strength: 500 mg",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Geltab, oral: 500 mg",
